Please try adding this to the kernel command-line:

`acpi_osi=Linux acpi_backlight=vendor`

(At the language boot menu, press TAB, then space, then the suggested arguments, then ENTER.)


Alternatively, create a `~/.xmodmaprc` and write into it:

	keycode 239=XF86KbdBrightnessDown
	keycode 123=XF86KbdBrightnessUp

... then run `xmodmap ~/.xmodmaprc`.

"""]]
